-- Pirelli May Acquire Plants in Russia, Berlusconi Says After Meeting Putin
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-04-26T12:16:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/pirelli-may-expand-presence-in-russia-berlusconi-says-after-putin-meeting.html

          
          
             Pirelli & C. SpA is in talks to
expand its presence and buy plants in Russia, Italian Prime
Minister Silvio Berlusconi said at a press conference with
Russian Prime Minister Vladimir Putin outside Milan today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
